::KitKat3::
She looked at Drillbit. "It's...it's nothing."  She smiled at him and 
put her hand on his shoulder. "UH, got a question. When are we going 
to attack the maximals?"

::Feline::
She about jumped out of her new skin. "Your where? Of all the 
places....Why are you there? How come your not here with the 
Allience? Why are you in a maximal base? OH for crying out loud. Get 
your rocket boosted backside over here and we'll talk. Oh, by the 
way. I got a new look. Hope you like it."
